en: Trading bot is a fast trading product specially provided for Mixin users. This product has more personalized revenue statistics and richer order types. Easily trade token on BigONE without registration.
zh: Trading Bot 为 Mixin 用户提供了更便捷的现货交易、更个性的收益统计、更丰富的订单类型和自动化低买高卖的网格交易量化策略。无需注册即可轻松交易 BigONE 上的币种。
